social_posts.post_text: Yellowstone dreams brought to you by Pepsi. 🤠
An all blue ensemble 💙
I’m forever grateful to everyone who has helped me along the way. ❤️

Oh this gets me SO excited. 

Everything I’ve ever wanted in a musical & more. We’re coming back BIGGER and BETTER. A new season with a whole new style. Schmicago. The Emmy award winning comedy series Schmigadoon is back April 5th on @appletvplus! 

Magical moves by the one and only @cgattelli & @bethebestonbroadway 🪄 It’s bananas!!!! Super grateful to be apart of this spectacular show.

Spirited was so freakin’ cool to be a part of. Being around so much talent in front of and behind the screen made me push to be better everyday. A huge thank you to @chloearnoldtaps @avaflav1 and @nichols14 for letting me live out my musical dreams. I’ve always wanted to be a part of something like this. I’m so grateful. 

Also, a huge shoutout to my dance teacher @dannyjpoland. He’s pushed me to be as versatile as possible in dance and I wouldn’t be where I am today without him. 🥹❤️
All the drammaaa.

schmigadoon s2 is out now on @appletvplus 

The biggest thank you to @cincopedia @cgattelli @jennie__ford @poshduck @dacosta_talent 💛

My face says it all. I had a blast judging the Toronto Kids Fashion Week auditions. I can’t wait to see these little stars rock the runway. ❤️
POV: You think you’re showing up to a work event. *I’m so lucky. 🥹❤️*

I wish 16 year old us could see us now. I think they’d be super proud of how far we’ve come. Our story is my favourite to tell and I can’t wait to write the next 50 + years with you. Thank you for waiting for fifteen years for me to finally make the right choice. The choice that I will continue to make for the rest of my life to be with you. I love you. I promise to love you always and forever, 365 days of every single year. I am so excited to be your wife. 
09.28.23 ❤️
Hands down, best day of my life. I’m so in love with you ♾️
I want a pocket-sized @ameliahairandmakeup for Christmas. You’re a magician, Amelia.❤️ P.S. I love you mom.
✨✨✨ moments before my happily ever after
I’m a wife. 🥹❤️ I really can’t believe that out of all the people in the world you chose to love me.
2023 was one for the books 🤍 I married my forever soulmate.
